          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The isomeric ratios  were  investigated  and  defined",
                " more  precisely  in simple photonuclear reactions at",
                " maximum energies of bremsstrahlung photons of  20  -",
                " 40  MeV for the targets in mass range 90 - 180.  The",
                " measurements results are compared with the estimates",
                " in  the  framework  of  the statistical model of the",
                " compound nucleus de-excitation."
              ]
            }
